text:
Despite its name ‘Ecosystem Restoration’ has mostly been Vegetation Ecology - establishing appropriate plants

More recent Community Ecology approaches emphasise the importance of other taxa

But Ecosystem Ecology needs applying more generally - ensuring functioning & resilience
